{"schema":"quality-calibration-case/v1","name":"micro-action-dialogue-and-low-density-pass","language":"zh-CN","targetType":"narrative-prose","split":"dev","genre":"family-realism","sourceKind":"third-party-fixture","modelFamily":"not-applicable","lengthBucket":"short","pov":"mixed","dialogueRatio":0.2,"text":"他回到家时，父亲正在院里绑车绳。父亲的手停了一下，又把绳子拉紧。『你等我一下，我去修完鸡圈门。』傍晚，他把石头看了一眼，装进外套口袋。","expectedRuleIds":[],"provenance":{"source":"worldwonderer/oh-story-claudecode","license":"MIT","commit":"3419e939b8455400cadcdd062fb1da2a92a6d4b9"}}
