{"schema":"quality-calibration-case/v1","name":"cliche-density-hit","language":"zh-CN","targetType":"narrative-prose","split":"dev","genre":"urban","sourceKind":"third-party-fixture","modelFamily":"not-applicable","lengthBucket":"short","pov":"mixed","dialogueRatio":0,"text":"夜色笼罩城市，霓虹隐约闪烁。林澈心中涌起一股情绪，仿佛预兆正在缓缓靠近。苏晚眼中闪过一丝复杂神色，嘴角勾起一抹笑意。她声音不大，却带着不容置疑的力量。林澈深吸一口气，淡淡开口，语气平静无波。苏晚指节泛白，目光锐利，沉默在两人之间蔓延。","expectedRuleIds":["zh-f3-cliche-density"],"provenance":{"source":"worldwonderer/oh-story-claudecode","license":"MIT","commit":"3419e939b8455400cadcdd062fb1da2a92a6d4b9"}}
{"schema":"quality-calibration-case/v1","name":"cliche-quoted-and-low-density-pass","language":"zh-CN","targetType":"narrative-prose","split":"dev","genre":"urban","sourceKind":"third-party-fixture","modelFamily":"not-applicable","lengthBucket":"short","pov":"mixed","dialogueRatio":0.2,"text":"她在本子上抄了一句『仿佛某种预兆』，旁边画了个叉。窗外的雨泡软纸箱，她把文件抽出来，摊在暖气片旁边。","expectedRuleIds":[],"provenance":{"source":"worldwonderer/oh-story-claudecode","license":"MIT","commit":"3419e939b8455400cadcdd062fb1da2a92a6d4b9"}}
