{"schema":"quality-calibration-case/v1","name":"metaphor-quoted-and-low-density-pass","language":"zh-CN","targetType":"narrative-prose","split":"dev","genre":"urban","sourceKind":"third-party-fixture","modelFamily":"not-applicable","lengthBucket":"short","pov":"mixed","dialogueRatio":0.2,"text":"群头像换成黑底白字。她在本子上写下『像水一样』，又拿红笔划掉。雨声从棚顶漏下来，像有人慢慢倒豆子。","expectedRuleIds":[],"provenance":{"source":"worldwonderer/oh-story-claudecode","license":"MIT","commit":"3419e939b8455400cadcdd062fb1da2a92a6d4b9"}}
{"schema":"quality-calibration-case/v1","name":"reasoning-chain-density-hit","language":"zh-CN","targetType":"narrative-prose","split":"dev","genre":"urban-fantasy","sourceKind":"third-party-fixture","modelFamily":"not-applicable","lengthBucket":"short","pov":"mixed","dialogueRatio":0,"text":"他知道眼下的任务是稳住人群，也明白秩序会很快失控。这意味着广播必须谨慎，因为错误指令可能带来新的风险。真正的问题在于，他没有完整规则，却必须做出判断。在这种情况下，任何安慰都可能造成误导。他需要先确认谁还在外面，再确认哪些楼栋能进门。只有这样，他才可能控制局面。他清楚系统把责任交给了他，也就是说，他必须承担结果。他需要筛选信息，需要判断风险。想到这里，他意识到这是信息不足时的决策能力。","expectedRuleIds":["zh-f3-reasoning-chain-density"],"provenance":{"source":"worldwonderer/oh-story-claudecode","license":"MIT","commit":"3419e939b8455400cadcdd062fb1da2a92a6d4b9"}}
